{"tid":1587702,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"金義聖：韓國民主運動 成功在不屈服的意志","createTime":"2019-09-22T13:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T11:47:13.000Z","uid":284304,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2aaebc42bed572b7bc8fe6de948dc846e953dbfb","tid":1587702,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:46:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kQ5_kSKyEEU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkQ5_kSKyEEU&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBlm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=93155b3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kQ5_kSKyEEU</a><br />\n他說，香港現在的情況，令他想起30年前韓國的民主運動，不過當時韓國的情況是屬於內部事務，如今香港卻面臨複雜國際形勢，要解決問題只會更困難，他對此感到惋惜。<br />\n<br />\n金義聖又說，隨着示威變得愈來愈暴力，要想實現目標也確實會變得愈來愈困難。不過，<span style=\"color: red;\">考慮到香港市民所處的狀況和他們的心情，如果說「你們不要打架，不能有暴力」這種話，也是太傲慢了。</span><br />\n<br />\n對於自己身體力行支持香港示威活動，他直言：「如果說沒有擔心過（影響中國市場），肯定是說謊。」但他認為那都是將來的事，他不想因為將來的可能發生的事，而無視現在正在發生的事情。"},{"pid":"e75b078bbe6e3faff6dbe5da0622917ca133ac25","tid":1587702,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d721da2a7f85a62684a21b0e392c3832d76bddb3","tid":1587702,"uid":160176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:46:53.000Z","msg":"不屈服<br />\n不要恐懼<br />\n做可以做的事"},{"pid":"54ec078422a4c81fdcd11a8dac9120e2e0341b4f","tid":1587702,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:47:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dbcbe2922f61a1ac59abde391b0c33e2ee544e0","tid":1587702,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:49:04.000Z","msg":"左膠又要選擇性失明了"},{"pid":"c90668230cda45052bb022542a9ca085dff07251","tid":1587702,"uid":187861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:50:06.000Z","msg":"不屈服"},{"pid":"806ebdf50cf99705ce0eac582e3232b208a5d7dd","tid":1587702,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:50:17.000Z","msg":"香港同韓國人經歷過既黑暗時代比只係濕濕碎<br />\n韓國人就明白抗爭者啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f084b74070b6f551eed36ba0a28abe8d505da5f7","tid":1587702,"uid":238040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:20:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jiwan.lam/videos/10219552424504958/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjiwan.lam%2Fvideos%2F10219552424504958%2F&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBlm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=d3b6bfe5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jiwan.lam/videos/10219552424504958/</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">[MBC節目《Straight》香港部分 - 中文字幕全片]</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">//這不單是其他國家的事情，民主主義和自由本來就是人民該普遍享有的權利//</span><br />\n<br />\n早前金義聖先生到左香港，進行左取材同採訪，而他嘅節目《Straight》係昨天9月23日(一)播放<br />\n<br />\n節目組落左個title比呢部分，叫「香港的憤怒」，入面有講到警察嘅無差別暴力鎮壓、選擇性執法、媒體嘅影響、新屋嶺、真普選（雨傘革命）/ 現今香港嘅行政長官選舉方法等等，其實將今次反送中運動嘅前因後果，以及為何越演越烈嘅原因都剖析得幾深入<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">//不是因為有希望才堅持，而是因為堅持才有希望//</span><br />\n<br />\n感謝一班香港人組成團隊作義務翻譯，亦感謝有人連夜趕工上字幕，令所有香港人都可以睇到呢篇深入而有水準嘅報導，希望大家可以加油，堅持落去~!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">#光復香港時代革命 #香港人加油 #五大訴求缺一不可 #香港 #HongKong #HK #홍콩</span><br />\n<br />\n*歡迎大家share出去*"},{"pid":"57ba9590e89b0920711da7911a36bbd040dafbe5","tid":1587702,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"806ebdf50cf99705ce0eac582e3232b208a5d7dd","tid":1587702,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:50:17.000Z","msg":"香港同韓國人經歷過既黑暗時代比只係濕濕碎<br />\n韓國人就明白抗爭者啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:47:13.000Z","msg":"唔一定，如果你計埋我哋嘅祖先嚟講就唔係喇"}]}